messages.msg: Welcome to our site! If you are looking for prayer or someone to chat with, reply to this message or email us at prayer@fightlust.com

I want to repent of all sexual sins I pray for deliverance from the spirit of lust adultery harlotry masturbation homosexuality perversion fornication sesuality lewdness and all acts of sexual sin to leave me and never return I renounce the ways I have used my body as an instrument of unrighteous I come against the spirit of rebellion and disobedience in my soul I ask God to release me from the spirit of worldliness and idolatry and coveting and fill me with his presence and holiness

It's wonderful that you're seeking deliverance and repentance. I encourage you to pray with sincerity and faith. You can use the following prayer as a guide:

"Heavenly Father, I come before you today, renouncing all sexual sins and asking for deliverance from the spirit of lust, adultery, harlotry, masturbation, homosexuality, perversion, fornication, sexuality, lewdness, and all acts of sexual sin. I ask that these spirits leave me and never return. I renounce the ways I have used my body as an instrument of unrighteousness. I come against the spirit of rebellion and disobedience in my soul. Please release me from the spirit of worldliness, idolatry, and coveting, and fill me with your presence and holiness."

Remember, you are not alone in this journey. If you need further support or resources, feel free to ask!

I release these idols from my life and I ask God to open my spiritual eyes to his truth and his path I renounce stagnation and being led by my flesh I ask God to kill all that's fleshly and worldly in me

It's powerful that you're taking these steps to release idols and seek God's truth. You can continue your prayer with these thoughts:

"Heavenly Father, I release these idols from my life and ask that you open my spiritual eyes to your truth and your path. I renounce stagnation and being led by my flesh. Please kill all that is fleshly and worldly in me, and fill me with your Spirit to guide me in righteousness."

Stay committed to this journey, and remember that healing and transformation take time. If you need further support or guidance, I'm here to help!
I ask for release and deliverance from the stronghold of harlotry and adultery I ask for cleansing of my will and soul and temple from the defilement of fornication i give all these sins to God

It's commendable that you're seeking release and deliverance from these strongholds. You can express your prayer like this:

"Heavenly Father, I ask for release and deliverance from the stronghold of harlotry and adultery. I seek cleansing of my will, soul, and temple from the defilement of fornication. I give all these sins to you, trusting in your power to heal and restore me."

Continue to lean on God for strength and guidance in your journey towards healing. If you need further support or resources, feel free to ask!
I pray for the spirit to help me to have eyes for my wife and only my wife I repent for all the ways I have offended God with my sinful lifestyle hypocrisy and impure thoughts

That's a heartfelt prayer, and it's important to bring these concerns before God. You might pray like this:

"Heavenly Father, I pray for the Spirit to help me have eyes for my wife and only my wife. I repent for all the ways I have offended You with my sinful lifestyle, hypocrisy, and impure thoughts. Please cleanse my heart and renew my spirit."

Remember, seeking God's help and guidance is a vital step in your journey. If you need additional prayers or resources, I'm here to assist you!
I pray for renewed sexual purity and pure thoughts I invite Jesus in my sexuality and into my life and ask him to reveal his true purpose and will for my I pray for a renewed Godly love for my wife

That's a beautiful prayer for renewal and guidance. You can express it like this:

"Heavenly Father, I pray for renewed sexual purity and pure thoughts. I invite Jesus into my sexuality and my life, asking Him to reveal His true purpose and will for me. I also pray for a renewed Godly love for my wife."

Continue to seek God's presence in your life, and trust that He will guide you on this journey. If you need further support or resources, just let me know!
Lastly I repent for all the ways I have hurt God and the faith community through my actions

It's important to acknowledge and repent for the ways we've hurt God and others. You might pray this:

"Heavenly Father, I repent for all the ways I have hurt You and the faith community through my actions. Please forgive me and help me to make amends as I seek to live a life that honors You."

Your sincerity in seeking forgiveness is a significant step towards healing. If you need more support or resources, feel free to reach out!

I pray for deliverance from any spirits that have tried or have attached themselves to me through sexual sins I release myself from any demonic controls through sexual sin and I send them to the cross and I pray I never allowed them back in

That's a powerful prayer for deliverance. You can express it like this:

"Heavenly Father, I pray for deliverance from any spirits that have tried or have attached themselves to me through sexual sins. I release myself from any demonic controls through these sins and send them to the cross. I pray that I never allow them back into my life."

Continue to trust in God's power to free you from these strongholds. If you need further guidance or support, I'm here to help!
I pray that I will start living by God's word and not my flesh or Satan

That's a wonderful prayer for strength and guidance. You might say:

"Heavenly Father, I pray that I will start living by Your Word and not by my flesh or the temptations of Satan. Help me to seek You daily and to rely on Your strength to overcome."

Remember, seeking God's guidance is a vital part of your journey. If you need more resources or support, just let me know!
